==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: dă shì téng, mà shì ài
===Etymology===
Literally: beating and cursing show one's love
===Proverb===
'''[[打]][[是]][[疼]]，[[罵]][[是]][[愛]]'''
# Sometimes harsh words or deeds can demonstrate one's love; Tough love is sometimes the only way.
===Alternate forms===
[[打是疼，骂是爱]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
